Problem statement
Aryan and his friends are very fond of patterns. For a given integer ‘N’, they want to make the Increasing Letter Triangle.

Example:
Input: ‘N’ = 3

Output: 

A
A B
A B C
Detailed explanation ( Input/output format, Notes, Images )
Constraints :
1  <= N <= 20
Time Limit: 1 sec
Sample Input 1:
3
Sample Output 1:
A
A B
A B C
Sample Input 2 :
4
Sample Output 2 :
A
A B
A B C 
A B C D
Sample Input 3 :
7
Sample Output 3 :
A
A B
A B C 
A B C D
A B C D E
A B C D E F
A B C D E F G



code:

void nLetterTriangle(int n) {
    for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
        for(int j=0;j<=i;j++)
        cout<<char(65+j)<<" ";
        cout<<endl;
    }
}
